
PACKAGING
=========

from cvs
--------

create a tarball

	cvs checkout gromosXX
	cd gromosXX
	./Config.sh
	mkdir BUILD
	cd BUILD
	../configure
	make dist

from tarball : preparation
--------------------------

take care to use a clean environment
	bash -h
	export PATH=/usr/bin:/bin

	tar zxvf gromosXX-X.Y.Z.tar.gz
	cd gromosXX-X.Y.Z
	./configure --prefix=/usr/local/gromos/gromosXX
	make
	
	make DESTDIR=/scratch/igcpc01/markus/tmp/package/gromosXX install
	

DEBIAN
------

	check libraries (ldd md)
	check package names of libraries 
	( apt-cache search pattern
	  dpkg -S filename
	)

	in the DESTDIR create a DEBIAN directory
	copy the control.debian file to DESTDIR/DEBIAN/control
	
	edit the dependencies

	dpkg --build gromosXX


